response.original_title: Milky Chance - Live from Vienna (FM4 Session)
response.overview: This is the full live recording from the Milky Chance show with the ORF Symphonic Orchestra in Vienna on November 17, 2023.  "After ten years of our band's journey, it was exciting to give our music a new form and let the songs shine anew. Instead of merely accompanying our tracks with an orchestra, we aimed to create a cohesive band experience. Through the new arrangements, we have built a bridge between modern electronic music and the classical orchestral world. It has exceeded our expectations, and we are very happy to have had this opportunity." -Milky Chance
response.title: Milky Chance - Live from Vienna (FM4 Session)
